description:
John Cougar Mellencamp - Live in Dallas - 1988



From An Unofficial Release, Very Originally Titled "Hurts So Good",
Here's John Cougar Mellencamp Playing At The Los Anados Hotel In Dallas,
Texas. This Was On March, 4 1988 During The Lonesome Jubilee Tour.
In 1988, Rolling Stone Magazine Called This Version Of Mellencamp's Band
"One Of The Most Powerful And Versatile Live Bands Ever Assembled."
